timelineManager.model

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • timelineManager.model.Task

  • public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a Task, it holds information such as title, description, start date, end date. It also has a color parameter that will be used in the TimelineManager. It's preparared with a priority value that are to be used in future releases. All tasks will be given a unique id number by a static counter.
